/mutelist: shows list of players that you've muted=/mutelist: shows list of players that you've muted
/mute playername: mutes playername. It means he can't send you pm=/mute playername: mutes playername. It means he can't send you pm
/unmute playername: unmutes playername. It means muted player can send you pm again=/unmute playername: unmutes playername. It means muted player can send you pm again
/setemail EmailAddress: sets you're email=/setemail EmailAddress: sets you're email
/me msg: says a me message.=/me msg: says a me message.
/pm playername messsage: sends them a private message =/pm playername messsage: sends them a private message 
/r message: replys to the last person who sent you a message. and you can use /reply zone. Also if you wanna leave you can use /leavefight=/r message: replys to the last person who sent you a message. and you can use /reply zone. Also if you wanna leave you can use /leavefight
 /staff: shows you game staff= /staff: shows you game staff
 /admintell message: Sends a message to current online admins. = /admintell message: Sends a message to current online admins. 
/rules: View the game's rules.=/rules: View the game's rules.
/events: Sends you a message with all the events on the server.=/events: Sends you a message with all the events on the server.
/joinevent ID:  joins an event.=/joinevent ID:  joins an event.
/leaveevent: leaves the current event if you joined any.=/leaveevent: leaves the current event if you joined any.
/nicknamefind playername: finds playername's nickname=/nicknamefind playername: finds playername's nickname
/afk: turns on or off you're afk=/afk: turns on or off you're afk
/bid amount: bids the amount of item that auctioner requested if there's any auction available=/bid amount: bids the amount of item that auctioner requested if there's any auction available
/currentauction: it tells you whats in the auction currently=/currentauction: it tells you whats in the auction currently
/playtime: checks total playtime of everyone=/playtime: checks total playtime of everyone
/vote yes: you say yes to current voting=/vote yes: you say yes to current voting
/vote no: you say no to current voting=/vote no: you say no to current voting
/pvp: toggles your pvp mode=/pvp: toggles your pvp mode
/suicide: you can suicide to safe zone with this command only when you are in the public maps=/suicide: you can suicide to safe zone with this command only when you are in the public maps
/teamcreate teamname: create: a team with a random password=/teamcreate teamname: create: a team with a random password
/teammembers: Lists your team's members.=/teammembers: Lists your team's members.
/teampoints: shows how much points your team have=/teampoints: shows how much points your team have
/teamkills: shows how much kills your team have=/teamkills: shows how much kills your team have
/getteampass: gets your team's password. Only works if you are leader of the team.=/getteampass: gets your team's password. Only works if you are leader of the team.
/changeteampass <password>: changes your team's password. Only works if you are leader of the team.=/changeteampass <password>: changes your team's password. Only works if you are leader of the team.
/changeteamleader <name>: changes your team's leader if you are the leader of the team.=/changeteamleader <name>: changes your team's leader if you are the leader of the team.
/teamkick <playername>: removes a player from your team.=/teamkick <playername>: removes a player from your team.
/teamcancel: cancels your team=/teamcancel: cancels your team
/teamleave: leaves a team you are in, if you're not the leader. If you are the leader use cancel.=/teamleave: leaves a team you are in, if you're not the leader. If you are the leader use cancel.
/t <message>: sends a message to your team.=/t <message>: sends a message to your team.
/jointeam <teamname> <teampassword>: Joins a team.=/jointeam <teamname> <teampassword>: Joins a team.
/team playername: shows in what team the player is=/team playername: shows in what team the player is
/zones: checks for trackable zones in your map=/zones: checks for trackable zones in your map
/trust playername: trusts the playername and he'll be able to check your map or looking at you=/trust playername: trusts the playername and he'll be able to check your map or looking at you
/untrust playername: untrusts the player name. It means he can't check your location and look at you=/untrust playername: untrusts the player name. It means he can't check your location and look at you
/look playername: looks the player=/look playername: looks the player
/lookstop: stops looking at who you were looking=/lookstop: stops looking at who you were looking
/setonlinemsg message: sets your online message=/setonlinemsg message: sets your online message
/setofflinemsg message: sets your offline message=/setofflinemsg message: sets your offline message
/go x y z: move you in to given coordinates in your map=/go x y z: move you in to given coordinates in your map
/channelusers: shows who is in your current language channel=/channelusers: shows who is in your current language channel
/recieve paid item name amount: give you the paid items that you've transfered to the server=/recieve paid item name amount: give you the paid items that you've transfered to the server
/setstatus message: set your status message=/setstatus message: set your status message
/clearstatus: clear your status message=/clearstatus: clear your status message
/status playername: gets status of the player name=/status playername: gets status of the player name
/pvplist: shows all pvp players=/pvplist: shows all pvp players
