You basically have to run away from incoming fires! They move toward you and if you don't run fast enough they'll hit and kill you! Once you beat a fire, you are reset to 0 and it gets faster! Hit left to move left, right to move right, c to check your position, and escape to quit.=You basically have to run away from incoming fires! They move toward you and if you don't run fast enough they'll hit and kill you! Once you beat a fire, you are reset to 0 and it gets faster! Hit left to move left, right to move right, c to check your position, and escape to quit.
